(1820,168,'service_description','When your water heater fails, hot showers become cold memories and daily routines grind to a halt. Whether you need emergency water heater repair, routine maintenance, or complete water heater replacement, Sunnyside AC provides expert service for all types of water heating systems including traditional tank water heaters, tankless water heaters, heat pump water heaters, and solar water heaters.\n\nOur certified technicians diagnose and repair common water heater problems including no hot water, insufficient hot water, strange noises, leaks, rusty water, and pilot light issues. We service all major brands including Rheem, AO Smith, Bradford White, Rinnai, Navien, and more. From simple thermostat adjustments to complete tank replacements, we handle every aspect of residential water heater service.\n\nIn South Florida\'s hard water conditions, water heaters face unique challenges including mineral buildup, corrosion, and reduced efficiency. Regular maintenance including tank flushing, anode rod inspection, and pressure relief valve testing extends equipment life and ensures reliable hot water for your family. Whether you\'re upgrading to energy-efficient tankless technology or need emergency repair of your existing system, we provide honest recommendations and quality workmanship backed by our satisfaction guarantee.'),
