exibility for Any Home</h2>\n\n  <p>One of the most compelling advantages of the Daikin FIT is its installation versatility. Traditional HVAC units require significant ground space and specific clearances for proper airflow and maintenance access. The FIT\'s compact footprint and innovative design options eliminate many of these constraints:</p>\n\n  <h3>Wall Mounting Options</h3>\n  <p>The unit can be mounted on exterior walls, preserving valuable ground space for landscaping, patios, or play areas. This is particularly valuable for homes with small yards or those looking to maintain a pristine outdoor appearance.</p>\n\n  <h3>Elevated Installation</h3>\n  <p>Unlike traditional units that must sit on concrete pads at ground level, the FIT can be installed elevated off the ground, providing protection from flooding, lawn equipment, and pest activity. This elevation also improves airflow and can enhance system efficiency.</p>\n\n  <h3>Tight Space Solutions</h3>\n  <p>Perfect for narrow side yards, small courtyards, or other challenging spaces where traditional units simply wouldn\'t fit. The compact design opens up possibilities for home additions, renovations, and new construction projects where space is at a premium.</p>\n\n  <h2>Professional Installation by Certified Experts</h2>\n\n  <p>At Sunnyside AC, our factory-trained technicians specialize in Daikin FIT installations and understand the unique requirements for optimal performance. We\'ll assess your home\'s specific needs, space constraints, and comfort requirements to design the perfect FIT solution for your property. Our expert installation ensures you\'ll enjoy all the benefits of this revolutionary system, from maximum efficiency to whisper-quiet operation.</p>\n\n  <h2>Serving South Florida Communities</h2>\n\n  <p>Sunnyside AC proudly serves homeowners throughout Miami-Dade, Broward, and Palm Beach counties with expert Daikin FIT installation, maintenance, and repair services. Our local knowledge of South Florida\'s climate challenges, building codes, and community requirements ensures your installation will be perfect for your specific situation.</p>\n\n  <h2>Industry-Leading Warranty and Support</h2>\n\n  <p>All these features combined make the Daikin FIT one of the most efficient and comfortable HVAC systems available today! Additionally, all Daikin products come with an industry-leading 12-year parts limited warranty so you can rest assured that your system will continue to work as designed for years to come.</p>\n\n  <h2>Transform Your Home with Daikin FIT</h2>\n\n  <p>With its powerful features and top-of-the-line technology, the Daikin FIT is an ideal choice for anyone looking to maximize their home\'s heating and cooling capabilities without sacrificing outdoor space or dealing with noisy equipment. Whether you\'re building a new home, replacing an outdated system, or upgrading to better efficiency, the FIT delivers the perfect combination of performance, quiet operation, and compact design.</p>\n\n  <section class=\"cta-section bg-gradient-to-r from-[#fb9939] to-[#e5462f] rounded-[20px] p-8 md:p-12 text-center\">\n    <h2 class=\"text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-4\">Need Daikin FIT System Service?</h2>\n    <p class=\"text-xl text-white/90 mb-8 max-w-2xl mx-auto\">\n      Call us now for expert Daikin FIT installation, repair, or maintenance. Compact HVAC system specialists ready 24/7.\n    </p>\n    <div class=\"flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center\">\n      <a href=\"tel:<?php echo esc_attr( SUNNYSIDE_TEL_HREF ); ?>\"\n         class=\"inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 rounded-[35px] bg-white px-8 py-4 transition-all hover:scale-105 hover:shadow-xl focus:ring-2 focus:ring-white focus:ring-offset-2 focus:ring-offset-orange-500 focus:outline-none\">\n        <span class=\"text-lg font-bold text-orange-500\">\n          Call <?php echo esc_html( SUNNYSIDE_PHONE_DISPLAY ); ?>\n        </span>\n      </a>\n\n      <a href=\